---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const meta = {
  title: "Disclaimer | NumbKit",
  description: "NumbKit tools are for informational purposes only. Crypto tools do not constitute financial advice; freelance tax tools do not replace a licensed accountant.",
  canonical: "https://numbkit.com/disclaimer/",
  lang: "en",
  slug: "disclaimer",
};
const schemaOrg = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebPage",
  "name": "Disclaimer",
  "url": "https://numbkit.com/disclaimer/",
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "NumbKit",
    "url": "https://numbkit.com"
  }
};
---
<BaseLayout meta={meta} schemaOrg={schemaOrg}>
  <article style="max-width:720px;margin:2rem auto;color:var(--color-muted);line-height:1.8;padding:0 1rem">
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: 27 April 2026</em></p>

    <p>All tools and content on NumbKit are provided for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. Nothing on this website constitutes financial, investment, tax, or legal advice. NumbKit is not affiliated with any exchange, protocol, brokerage, or financial institution mentioned in our tools.</p>

    <h2>Crypto Tools Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>Cryptocurrency markets are highly volatile and inherently risky. Past performance does not guarantee future results. Calculators on this site (arbitrage, impermanent loss, breakeven, bridge fees, ROI, tax-loss harvesting) provide <strong>theoretical estimates</strong> based on the inputs you provide and the formulas described in our <a href="/methodology/">Methodology</a>.</p>

    <p>NumbKit does not guarantee the availability of liquidity, the accuracy of real-time price quotes obtained from third-party APIs, or the reliability of any centralized or decentralized exchange. The user acknowledges that crypto trading depends on execution speed, network conditions (gas fees, congestion, L2 sequencer status), and protocol-specific behaviour beyond our control.</p>

    <p>Real-world trading outcomes will differ from calculator results due to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Slippage and execution latency on live markets</li>
      <li>Sudden price movements during the trade window</li>
      <li>Exchange-specific fees, withdrawal limits, and VIP tiers</li>
      <li>Smart-contract risk on DeFi protocols</li>
      <li>L2 sequencer downtime or transaction reordering</li>
      <li>Failed transactions, gas spikes, or front-running</li>
      <li>Regulatory changes in your jurisdiction</li>
    </ul>
    <p>NumbKit shall not be held responsible for impermanent losses, margin liquidations, failed executions, missed-opportunity costs, or any other damages arising from the use of our theoretical estimates. You alone are responsible for your trading decisions. Never invest funds you cannot afford to lose. Before acting on any calculation, consult a licensed financial advisor in your country.</p>

    <h2>Freelance Finance Tools — Aviso Legal</h2>
    <p>Las calculadoras de finanzas freelance (tarifa real por hora, impuestos para nómadas digitales, IVA en infoproductos, ahorro jubilación, LTV, ROI de herramientas SaaS) entregan <strong>estimaciones orientativas</strong> basadas en los datos que usted ingresa y en la información regulatoria publicada por los organismos oficiales de cada país (DIAN, AFIP, SII, entre otros) en la fecha de la última revisión manual indicada en nuestra <a href="/methodology/">página de metodología</a>.</p>

    <p>Los valores de referencia (categorías de Monotributo argentino, UVT colombiana, retención chilena, entre otros) son ilustrativos y pueden quedar desactualizados entre revisiones trimestrales debido a decretos, resoluciones administrativas o cambios legislativos. <strong>Es responsabilidad exclusiva del usuario verificar los valores vigentes</strong> en los portales oficiales (afip.gob.ar, dian.gov.co, sii.cl) antes de realizar liquidaciones impositivas, emitir facturas o presentar declaraciones.</p>

    <p>Estos resultados <strong>no reemplazan el asesoramiento de un contador, abogado o asesor fiscal habilitado</strong>. Las normas tributarias varían según provincia, municipio, categoría profesional y situación personal del contribuyente. Antes de tomar decisiones fiscales con impacto económico relevante, consulte a un profesional matriculado en su jurisdicción.</p>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>Some external links on NumbKit are affiliate links (primarily to Binance). If you sign up through them, NumbKit may receive a commission at no additional cost to you. This relationship does not influence our methodology or calculator outputs. See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

    <h2>Digital Products — Gumroad as Merchant of Record</h2>
    <p>When you purchase a digital product from NumbKit, the transaction is processed by <strong>Gumroad Inc.</strong>, who acts as the Merchant of Record. Gumroad is responsible for collecting and remitting any applicable VAT or sales tax according to your jurisdiction, and is the data controller for purchase information. NumbKit does not receive or store your payment data. Refunds, billing disputes, and tax invoices are handled directly by Gumroad according to their <a href="https://gumroad.com/terms" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Terms of Service</a>.</p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, in no event shall NumbKit, its operator (Leticia Verónica Minujen), affiliates, or representatives be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, exemplary, or punitive damages — including, without limitation, loss of profits, loss of data, opportunity costs, trading losses, tax penalties, regulatory fines, or other intangible losses — arising out of or in any way connected with your use of, or inability to use, the calculators or content on this site, even if NumbKit has been advised of the possibility of such damages.</p>

    <p>For free tools, NumbKit's total aggregate liability shall not exceed <strong>zero (USD 0)</strong>, reflecting the absence of any commercial transaction between the user and NumbKit for the use of these calculators. For paid digital products purchased through Gumroad, any liability is limited to the purchase price actually paid for the specific product, and is governed by Gumroad's Terms of Service in their capacity as Merchant of Record.</p>

    <p>Some jurisdictions do not allow the exclusion or limitation of certain damages. In those jurisdictions, the limitations above shall apply to the maximum extent permitted by law.</p>

    <h2>No Warranty</h2>
    <p>NumbKit is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties of any kind, express or implied, including but not limited to warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, non-infringement, or accuracy. We make reasonable efforts to keep formulas, fee structures, and regulatory data accurate and current, but we do not guarantee error-free results. To report an error, write to <strong>contact@numbkit.com</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Governing Law</h2>
    <p>This disclaimer is governed by the laws of the Republic of Argentina. Any dispute arising from the use of NumbKit shall be subject to the jurisdiction of the ordinary courts of the Autonomous City of Buenos Aires, without prejudice to any non-waivable consumer-protection rights granted to the user by the laws of their country of residence.</p>

    <h2>Related Documents</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/methodology/">Methodology</a> — how each calculator works</li>
      <li><a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> — how we handle data</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
